---
title: Open-Faced Pesto Chickpea Melts with Balsamic Dressed Salad
description: Inspired by the classic Caprese salad, this riff takes the form of an open-faced sandwich, layered with melty mozzarella, zingy basil pesto and chickpeas, for added protein!
